OL,3,CGuinea pigs on the loose! JSPCA's
OL,4,Csearch for pets' owner
OL,6,FSeven guinea pigs have been rescued in
OL,7,FJersey after they were spotted on the
OL,8,Floose near Devil's Hole.
OL,10,FThe JSPCA responded to a call earlier
OL,11,Ftoday and after initially being able
OL,12,Fto catch three of them, were able to
OL,13,Ftrack down the remaining four later
OL,14,Fthis afternoon.
OL,16,FThe shelter say they do not know where
OL,17,Fthe guinea pigs came from but are
OL,18,Fasking any islanders with any
OL,19,Finformation to give them a call as
OL,20,Fthey would like to find the owner as
OL,21,Fsoon as possible.
